column5: a little early yet but managed this little guy after 3 hours of casting on sept 10 didnt measure it just wanted a quick picture and a quick release
Good job on the ski!  What region? Gbay/Kawartha/Niagara
Nice Musky!Looks shaped like a torpedo, must have been an acrobatic fight! Thanks for sharing.
Great report and pic FinS  Nice ski.....Congrats Thanks for sharing Leechman
Great catch!!! You gotta love it when the temps come down a bit and the big fish are catchable from shore.  I hope to see more successful shore outings!!
Judging by the water colour, and his location, it's pretty safe to say its a St. Clair fish
Great job man.  It must be a real thrill and sense of accomplishment to catch one from shore.  Congratulations.
